open_message: Hello there! Thanks for reaching out to ChivMail here on the official Chivalry 2 Discord server. A moderator will get to your message as soon as they are able. If you are enquiring about an in-game mute or ban, please open a ticket on the support site instead: https://support.chivalry2.com/.
close_message: If you want to contact the mods about something else, send another message to open a new ticket.
